# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok america 's trade deficit widened by more than $ ### billion last year , reaching a record of $ ###.# billion , the government said friday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01))
      :ARG1 (w / widen-01
            :ARG1 (d / deficit
                  :mod (t / trade-01)
                  :poss (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "America")))
            :ARG2 (m / more-than
                  :op1 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                        :quant 1000000000
                        :unit (d2 / dollar)))
            :time (y / year
                  :mod (l / last))
            :ARG0-of (r / reach-01
                  :ARG1 (r2 / record
                        :mod m2)))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok <unk> of british police swooped on addresses in england and wales on tuesday , arresting seven people after a year-long international probe to smash an alleged human trafficking network accused of smuggling indian nationals into britain via france .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (s / swoop-01
            :ARG0 (p / police
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Great"
                              :op2 "Britain")))
            :ARG1 (a2 / address
                  :location (a3 / and
                        :op1 (c2 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "England"))
                        :op2 (c3 / country
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Wales"))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / tuesday)))
      :op2 (a4 / arrest-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (p2 / person
                  :quant 7)
            :time (a5 / after
                  :op1 (p3 / probe-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (n4 / network
                              :ARG0-of (t2 / traffic-01
                                    :ARG1 (h / human))
                              :ARG1-of (a6 / allege-01)
                              :ARG1-of (a7 / accuse-01
                                    :ARG2 (s2 / smuggle-01
                                          :ARG0 n4
                                          :ARG1 p2
                                          :mod (n5 / nation)
                                          :mod (c4 / country
                                                :name (n6 / name
                                                      :op1 "India")))
                                    :ARG3 c
                                    :path (c5 / country
                                          :name (n7 / name
                                                :op1 "France")))))
                  :mod (ii / international)
                  :duration (t3 / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 1
                        :unit (y / year)))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a final report on the estonia car ferry disaster , due out this autumn , will be delayed until next year , the international commission investigating the accident said wednesday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (c / commission
            :mod (ii / international)
            :ARG0-of (ii2 / investigate-01
                  :ARG1 (a / accident)))
      :ARG1 (d / delay-01
            :ARG1 (r / report-01
                  :ARG1 (d2 / disaster
                        :mod (f / ferry
                              :mod (c2 / car)
                              :mod (e / estonia))
                        :mod (f2 / final)
                        :ARG1-of (d3 / due-03
                              :time (d4 / date-entity
                                    :season (a2 / autumn)
                                    :mod (y / year
                                          :mod (t / this))))))
            :time (u / until
                  :op1 y
                  :mod (n / next)))
      :time (w / wednesday))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok traffic safety office airs tv ads to warn drivers about how heat can lead tires to fail .

      :ARG0 (o / office
            :topic (s / safe-01
                  :ARG1 (t / traffic)))
      :ARG1 (a2 / advertise-01
            :medium (t2 / television))
      :purpose (w / warn-01
            :ARG0 o
            :ARG1 (p / possible-01
                  :ARG1 (l / lead-03
                        :ARG0 (h / heat)
                        :ARG1 (t3 / tire)
                        :ARG2 (f / fail-01
                              :ARG1 t3)))
            :ARG2 (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (d / drive-01))))

            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Bonn")
            :location (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Germany")))
      :time (w / weekend
            :mod (t / this))
      :purpose (b / bid-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (r / revive-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (t2 / talk-01
                        :ARG1 (c3 / climate
                              :mod (g / globe))
                        :ARG1-of (l / leave-12
                              :ARG2 (a / and
                                    :op1 (m4 / mangle-01)
                                    :op2 (m5 / moribund))
                              :time (a2 / after
                                    :op1 (s / summit
                                          :location (c4 / city
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Coptenhagen")))))))))

            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

                  :mod (d / defend-01)))
      :ARG1 (w / win-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (c3 / contract-02
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (a2 / assist-01
                        :ARG0 c
                        :ARG1 (g / government-organization
                              :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01
                                    :ARG1 (c4 / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "U.S."))))
                        :ARG2 (e / effort-01
                              :ARG0 g
                              :ARG1 (g3 / gather-01
                                    :ARG0 g
                                    :ARG1 (ii / intelligence
                                          :mod (f / foreign)))))
                  :ARG2 g)
            :ARG3 (m / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000000
                  :unit (d2 / dollar)))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

# ::id 8 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :op1 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of (c2 / criticize-01)
                        :mod (d / domestic))
                  :op2 (p4 / person
                        :ARG0-of (c3 / criticize-01)
                        :mod (f / foreign))
                  :mod (b / both))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday))
            :manner (a3 / accuse-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 a2
                  :ARG2 (p5 / prepare-02
                        :ARG0 a2
                        :ARG1 (c4 / cause-01
                              :ARG0 a2

                              :location c)))))

# ::alignments
(c / chair-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Yasser"
                  :op2 "Arafat")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c2 / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Palestine"))
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
      :ARG1 (m / meet-03
            :ARG0 (m2 / movement
                  :mod (f / fatah)
                  :poss p)
            :location (c3 / city
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Ciro"))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s / sunday))
            :purpose (d2 / discuss-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (f2 / fear-01
                        :ARG1 (p3 / process-02
                              :ARG1 (p4 / peace)
                              :location (w / world-region
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Middle"
                                          :op2 "East")))
                        :prep-under (p5 / person
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Benjamin"
                                    :op2 "Netanyahu")
                              :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 (c4 / country
                                          :name (n6 / name
                                                :op1 "Israel"))
                                    :ARG2 (m3 / minister
                                          :mod (p6 / prime))))))))
